        <hr noshade size="1">
        
        <font color="white" face="Verdana" size="2"> It's apparent with the changes that Verant have introduced over the last two or three patches that having reasonable resistance for day to day useage is much more important than it has been in the past (on non-PvP servers at least).</P><P>I'm hoping in this topic to have people suggest gear that is good enough for every day use, that has the additional bonus of +resist - players from PvP could probably just put a link to their Magelo profiles :)</P><P>Drexyll, I know that in another post you mention that you have resists of around 130+ - so feedback from you would be welcome.</P><P>Mentioning uber gear is ok, but I'm really interested in the more mundane gear that can be achieved by normal players (for the sake of argument lets assume a 10kpp bankroll).</P><P>For myself I'd like to set a target of around +100 unbuffed across the board. Maybe it's just a kneejerk reaction but being DoT'd silly by green goblins in Nurga makes me want to get a little proactive on this.</P><P>All comments welcome.</P><P><BR><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=236573" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.clement-evans.co.uk/xatan/xatan-eyes-heretic.jpg" border=0></a><BR></font></td>

