         Realistically, expect to take major hits on your hp/mana pool if you need to raise all saves above 100.  Only no-drop gear can offer resists and good stats.  Sure there are some nice droppable peices that give good resists and maybe some int, but be prepared to take a hit on your hp pool for sure.</P><P> If you are getting decent no-drop gear, your resists will be all over 100 anyway.</P><P><b><font color=blue>Retrievil Hesevil</font id=blue></b><BR><font color=red><b>58 DE Necromancer - Tallon Zek</font id=red></b><BR><font color=blue><b>56 Iksar Necromancer - Rodcet Nife</b></font id=blue><BR><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=333155" target="_blank">http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=333155</a><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
