         Cheers Folks.</P><P>Final Scores on the Doors. As an Iksar necro - our main weaknesses in resists are Fire and Magic, so this is why for example I skipped Blue diamond headgear in favour of the fire/cold froglok kings crown:</P><P><b>Purchased:</b></P><P><img src="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/equipment/graphics15/velium_blue_diamond_bracelet.jpg" border=0></P><P><img src="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/equipment/graphics10/CrownofFK.jpg" border=0></P><P><img src="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/equipment/graphics16/netted_kelp_lined_shoes.jpg" border=0></P><P><img src="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/equipment/graphics15/Students_Homework.jpg" border=0></P><P><BR><b>Want to obtain:</b></P><P><img src="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/equipment/graphics17/ceremonial_smudging_stick.jpg" border=0></P><P>The Cazicite +10 Every resist bracelet (can't find an image :)</P><P>The robe that gives me both Fire and Magic resists:</P><P><img src="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/equipment/graphics12/froglokbonecastersrobe.jpg" border=0> </P><P>..and I'll have to think about swapping out my stein of moggok and losing all that INT in favour of:</P><P><img src="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/equipment/graphics18/Star_Ruby_Encrusted_Stein.jpg" border=0></P><P>All of that still leaves me with my arms and legs to play with, so if I beef up on Int and mana there I'll have broken even on the mana front (maybe) and lost very little HP.</P><P>Thanks all - I'm sure there'll be a few people making use of the suggestions that you have imparted.</P><P><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=236573" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.clement-evans.co.uk/xatan/xatan-eyes-heretic.jpg" border=0></a><BR><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
