        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         Hmmm...strange...most Iksar I know have good fire resist, but bad cold resist.</P><P>There are a couple other things you can get in Maiden's which have nice resists, like Stone Idol and Medallion of Life (there's one more but I can never remember the name). Only downside is that they are no drop.</P><P>Bloodweave pantaloons have Int, HP (I think) and some resists, but knock 5 off FR. Thurg/SS leggings have resists on them too, but are relatiely rare. If you hunt in DN, then Flayed Paebala leggings have nice disease resists (20).</P><P>Oh you can also buy Diamond masks, gold for fire/cold (10) and electrum for disease/poison (10). They also give some boosts to all the other resists.</P><P>Tenaiya Soulscorcher<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
